      "message": "You should be able to log in to that jenkins instance with LF creds. \n\nMaybe instead of putting it directly just don't set the scripts in job definition but in templates directly? That is to move oom_build_script and  subproject_build_script vars definitions from jjb/oom/oom-helm.yaml to the template in jjb/global-templates-helm.yaml so that the scripts are defined for both helm3 and helm2 jobs in their respective templates and do not override those at job definition level.",
